<emphasis box="[372,454,1037,1063]" italics="true" pageId="29" pageNumber="30">bis, bi-</emphasis>
: two, and 
<emphasis box="[578,632,1037,1063]" italics="true" pageId="29" pageNumber="30">dens</emphasis>
: a tooth; with reference to the apertural dentition.
</paragraph>
